QuestData.Title: Ambushed!
QuestData.Description: This should have been a walk in the park. Their forces are hungry, injured and ill equipped. Yet somehow, we walked right into their trap.$B$BWe approached these reefs from the south to gain cover and were immediately boarded by the Alliance dogs.$B$BI'm sorry to say, if you want our cannons to fire at anything, you're going to have to help us take our ships back.
QuestData.LogDescription: Captain Harker aboard the Windrunner wants you to kill 15 North Fleet Marines.
QuestData.CompletionText: What are you waiting for? Kill the Alliance scum already!
QuestData.RewardText: Nice work paring those mongrels down to size. My men will be able to clean up the rest.
